### Producer

This dashboard provides visibility into the performance, throughput, and health of Kafka producers.

- Monitors key throughput metrics such as record send rate and outgoing bytes per second.
- Tracks record error and retry rates to identify potential message delivery issues.
- Provides insight into batching performance by tracking average and maximum batch and record sizes.
- Highlights potential bottlenecks by monitoring I/O wait time and available buffer memory.
